            <abstract id="ref1" label="Abstract">The collection includes material relating to government, mythology, festivals, customs, games, etc. of the Ojibwa Indians. Also includes comments on the language; vocabulary, some items with English glosses; lists of bands and locations; and photographs of people, activities, dwellings, canoes, etc.</abstract>
